    <content><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h4 id="1-Scrapy框架简介"><a href="#1-Scrapy框架简介" class="headerlink" title="1. Scrapy框架简介"></a>1. Scrapy框架简介</h4><ul>
<li>异步处理请求</li>
<li>自动调整爬取速度</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="en-resource://database/2890:1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="f7028787ed26c1057a3ebae4e1f67af9.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="f7028787ed26c1057a3ebae4e1f67af9.png" title="f7028787ed26c1057a3ebae4e1f67af9.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2890:1" class="lazyload"></a></p>
<h5 id="运行流程"><a href="#运行流程" class="headerlink" title="运行流程"></a>运行流程</h5><ol>
<li>传入url开始</li>
<li>引擎将url封装成请求传给下载器</li>
<li>下载器下载资源，返回响应</li>
<li>解析出item和url</li>
<li>item传入pipeline</li>
<li>url交给调度器继续爬取</li>
</ol>
<h5 id="包含组件"><a href="#包含组件" class="headerlink" title="包含组件"></a>包含组件</h5><ul>
<li>engine</li>
<li>Scheduler调度器</li>
<li>Downloader</li>
<li>Spiders</li>
<li>Pipeline</li>
<li>下载中间件(Middlewares)</li>
<li>爬虫中间件</li>
<li>调度中间件</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="2-安装"><a href="#2-安装" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装"></a>2. 安装</h4><p>先安装依赖：Twisted<br><code>pip install twisted</code></p>
<p>报错<br><code>'ReadTimeoutError("HTTPSConnectionPool(host='pypi.org', port=443): Read timed out. (read timeout=15)",)'</code><br>解决方法：换源<br><code>pip install twisted -i
https://pypi.douban.com/simple</code></p>
<h6 id="国内镜像"><a href="#国内镜像" class="headerlink" title="国内镜像"></a>国内镜像</h6><p>清华：<a href="https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</a><br>豆瓣：<a href="http://pypi.douban.com/simple/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://pypi.douban.com/simple/</a><br><code>pip install Scrapy -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</code><br><a href="en-resource://database/2892:1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="3057bbe4a07d3af230db1e6b87a0bce3.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="3057bbe4a07d3af230db1e6b87a0bce3.png" title="3057bbe4a07d3af230db1e6b87a0bce3.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2892:1" class="lazyload"></a><br>安装成功</p>
<h4 id="3-使用"><a href="#3-使用" class="headerlink" title="3. 使用"></a>3. 使用</h4><p>创建项目<code>scrapy startproject 项目名</code><br><a href="en-resource://database/2894:1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="722a532c8e0bc32d5520f6454609863f.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="722a532c8e0bc32d5520f6454609863f.png" title="722a532c8e0bc32d5520f6454609863f.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2894:1" class="lazyload"></a></p>
<p><a href="en-resource://database/2896:2" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" title="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2896:2" class="lazyload"></a></p>
<p><a href="en-resource://database/2898:1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" title="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2898:1" class="lazyload"></a><br><a href="en-resource://database/2896:2" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" title="a79b9d23dfeed987a8c172b8fda4e8c5.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2896:2" class="lazyload"></a><br><a href="en-resource://database/2898:1" data-fancybox="group" data-caption="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" class="fancybox"><img alt="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" title="24b4472a7ae7894da07e6a30c3e0aa37.png" data-src="en-resource://database/2898:1" class="lazyload"></a></p>
</body></html>]]></content>
